VGg\"> </a>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"caption-gallery\">\n       <p class=\"Image\"></p>\n       <p class=\"Normal\">Hạ tầng sân vận động Cần Thơ đã xuống cấp, chưa được đầu tư sửa chữa. Trong đó, đường chạy điền kinh hư hỏng nặng, cặp rãnh thoát nước xuất hiện lỗ thủng lớn chưa được khắc phục.</p>\n       <p></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </figure>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"banner-ads width_common mb20\" style=\"transition: all .6s ease-in-out;\">\n  <div class=\"lazier\" id=\"_break_page_2\" data-component-type=\"_break_page_ads\" data-key=\"2\"></div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"section-inner outset-column gallery-detail-photo\" id=\"gallery-34434845\">\n  <div class=\"medium-insert-embeds medium-insert-embeds-gallery medium-insert-embeds-normal medium-insert-embeds-large\">\n   <figure>\n    <div class=\"medium-insert-embed\">\n     <div class=\"width_common gallery_block gallery_block_full gallery_2item\">\n      <div class=\"inner_gallery owl-carousel\">\n       <div class=\"item_gallery\" data-component=\"true\" data-component-type=\"gallery\" data-component-value1=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2025/11/12/8-CHON-7JPG-1762876426-1762907690-1762907816-1762908068-1762909311-1762921847-1762923579-1762931824-1762931993-1762932262-1762934188-1762935113-1762937757-1762956091.jpg?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=3s3MgABEocMII-9ACyE4qg\" data-component-value2=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2025/11/12/8-CHON-7JPG-1762876426-1762907690-1762907816-1762908068-1762909311-1762921847-1762923579-1762931824-1762931993-1762932262-1762934188-1762935113-1762937757-1762956091.jpg?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=3s3MgABEocMII-9ACyE4qg\">\n        <a href=\"#\"> <img class=\"img_pc\" src=\"https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2025/11/12/8-CHON-7JPG-1762876426-1762907690-1762907816-1762908068-1762909311-1762921847-1762923579-1762931824-1762931993-1762932262-1762934188-1762935113-1762937757-1762956091.j